                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The secondary 56Ni beam was produced by",
                "projectile fragmentation of 160 MeV/A 58Ni primary",
                "beam on a thick 610 mg/cm2 9Be target. The 56Ni",
                "secondary beam was analysed using A1900 fragment",
                "separator and was unambiguously distinguished from",
                "all contaminants via the time-of-flight difference",
                "measured between two plastic scintillators located at",
                "the exit of the A1900 and the object position of the",
                "S800 analysis beam line."
